{"tid":1132384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生仔女都幾大洗費 筆數計極都唔掂","createTime":"2019-04-30T09:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T10:09:30.000Z","uid":54581,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"05f4a53ef0ce5c92224bf80c4e31134a4acd0c26","tid":1132384,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:14:04.000Z","msg":"（有錢有樓上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家都知 養仔女真係好大洗費<br />\n<br />\n學費生活費醫藥費 都未計其他林林種種洗費<br />\n<br />\n所以有樣野想請教下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底你地後生有幾廢柴，先會幾皮野流動資金都無？<br />\n<br />\n你地仔女問你拎錢交學費 有病想睇專科私家醫生個陣<br />\n你要左抄右抄幾個户口 最後同個仔講屋企無咁多錢個陣你有無覺得羞恥，無臉見個仔？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你覺唔覺幾皮野都拎唔到俾個仔，對於你黎講係一個恥辱？ 好似直接咁同自己個仔講你係碌廢物<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解你地咁撚廢 仲要生個仔出黎玩鳩自己玩鳩佢？<br />\n<br />\n你地唔撚plan過買樓儲錢就結婚 到底係出於咩原因？"},{"pid":"e9ed65211f681abdce97744c8d5121f6747dd372","tid":1132384,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:21:01.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7272e8e3f4149e23051ab9fcdb63aed2f8dab628","tid":1132384,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾十歲人連十幾萬都無既人真係好垃圾"},{"pid":"8c8366b2035290799b8b4b6c8419602aa79b23a7","tid":1132384,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7272e8e3f4149e23051ab9fcdb63aed2f8dab628","tid":1132384,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾十歲人連十幾萬都無既人真係好垃圾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T09:34:11.000Z","msg":"所以大家趁後生要識投資"},{"pid":"8f4c25359cef8212e8347cfde469f8086b9eb7cb","tid":1132384,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c8366b2035290799b8b4b6c8419602aa79b23a7","tid":1132384,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7272e8e3f4149e23051ab9fcdb63aed2f8dab628","tid":1132384,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":